cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the application of deep learning to robot touch. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper discusses optical tactile sensors and their use in bridging deep learning for vision to touch. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also possible categories as the paper discusses the use of deep learning to train accurate pose models. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses how accurate estimation of pose from touch can enable robots to safely and precisely control their physical interactions.
